data.title: Joan Crawford and Franchot Tone at premiere
data.meta_description: Title supplied by cataloger.; Photograph was edited for publication purposes.This event was the premiere for "The Good Earth," held at the Carthay Circle Theatre in Hollywood.Photograph caption dated January 30, 1937 reads, "Wearing her famed star sapphires and ermine coat, Joan Crawford is shown arriving down the 'peach blossom' lane with Franchot Tone, her husband."
